			"dazzle_poison_touch"		"Use it as harass tool early on. Remember that the effect&amp;apos;s duration will be refreshed with your every attack and it also stacks with itself. Combining with Bad Juju, you can use it as farming tool as well"
			"dazzle_shallow_grave"		"You don&amp;apos;t really need it early on, but having a value point still won&amp;apos;t hurt. You can use it on yourself while towerdiving early on and at later stages - to save allies, even all your team!"
			"dazzle_shadow_wave"		"Your main tool to keep laning forever. It&amp;apos;s also your farming tool and wave clearing tool.

It deals more damage with more units being healed by it. You can use it on lane against melee heroes (or ranged heroes who will walk across creepwave) and in fights you can combo it with your teammates or illusions/summons.

Try to spam it every time it&amp;apos;s off cooldown. At level 12 you shouldn&amp;apos;t have much mana issues and this spell will make your all team unstoppable."
			"special_bonus_unique_dazzle_2"		"You will be in the middle of a fight most of the time, so you don&amp;apos;t really need cast range, while additional heal/damage will give you way more value considering Shadow Wave spam"
